3194// Bits for subtarget features that participate in instruction matching.
3195enum SubtargetFeatureBits : uint8_t {
3196 Feature_HasSIMD128Bit = 6,
3197 Feature_HasUnimplementedSIMD128Bit = 9,
3198 Feature_HasAtomicsBit = 0,
3199 Feature_HasMultivalueBit = 3,
3200 Feature_HasNontrappingFPToIntBit = 4,
3201 Feature_NotHasNontrappingFPToIntBit = 10,
3202 Feature_HasSignExtBit = 7,
3203 Feature_HasTailCallBit = 8,
3204 Feature_HasExceptionHandlingBit = 2,
3205 Feature_HasBulkMemoryBit = 1,
3206 Feature_HasReferenceTypesBit = 5,
3207};
3208
3209#ifndef NDEBUG
3210static const char *SubtargetFeatureNames[] = {
3211 "Feature_HasAtomics",
3212 "Feature_HasBulkMemory",
3213 "Feature_HasExceptionHandling",
3214 "Feature_HasMultivalue",
3215 "Feature_HasNontrappingFPToInt",
3216 "Feature_HasReferenceTypes",
3217 "Feature_HasSIMD128",
3218 "Feature_HasSignExt",
3219 "Feature_HasTailCall",
3220 "Feature_HasUnimplementedSIMD128",
3221 "Feature_NotHasNontrappingFPToInt",
3222 nullptr
3223};
3224
3225#endif // NDEBUG
3226FeatureBitset WebAssemblyMCCodeEmitter::
3227computeAvailableFeatures(const FeatureBitset &FB) const {
3228 FeatureBitset Features;
3229 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureSIMD128])
3230 Features.set(Feature_HasSIMD128Bit);
3231 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureUnimplementedSIMD128])
3232 Features.set(Feature_HasUnimplementedSIMD128Bit);
3233 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureAtomics])
3234 Features.set(Feature_HasAtomicsBit);
3235 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureMultivalue])
3236 Features.set(Feature_HasMultivalueBit);
3237 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureNontrappingFPToInt])
3238 Features.set(Feature_HasNontrappingFPToIntBit);
3239 if (!FB[WebAssembly::FeatureNontrappingFPToInt])
3240 Features.set(Feature_NotHasNontrappingFPToIntBit);
3241 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureSignExt])
3242 Features.set(Feature_HasSignExtBit);
3243 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureTailCall])
3244 Features.set(Feature_HasTailCallBit);
3245 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureExceptionHandling])
3246 Features.set(Feature_HasExceptionHandlingBit);
3247 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureBulkMemory])
3248 Features.set(Feature_HasBulkMemoryBit);
3249 if (FB[WebAssembly::FeatureReferenceTypes])
3250 Features.set(Feature_HasReferenceTypesBit);
3251 return Features;
3252}

3259 CEFBS_HasBulkMemory,

3261 CEFBS_HasNontrappingFPToInt,
3262 CEFBS_HasReferenceTypes,
3263 CEFBS_HasSIMD128,
